Firstly, here is a rough overview of the various duties and responsibilities of the volunteers:

* Room setup - Prepping the main conference hall for the main conference, including laying out cables/power strips, arranging tables/chairs, and other physical labor. We will go to the venue after the boat ride.
* Writing day - Registering people and general information inquiries, most likely directions to various rooms and schedule questions, assist with other duties as assigned (managed by the writing day coordinator, <PERSON>)
